arStrings.szText:
Provides the opportunity for Subo to offer caches with {c_legendary}Legendary{/c} items with {c_important}Utility Aspects{/c} during{icon:Marker_Bartering, 2.4}{c_important}Bartering{/c}. 

{c_label}Bartering:{/c} This {c_important}Trade Agreement{/c} will go into effect on the Mercenary's next new stock delivery. It does not guarantee stock of these items. The more difficult the item is to obtain, the less frequent it will be offered.

{c_label}Aspects:{/c} {icon:Crafting_Blacksmith_SalvageItems, 1.8} {c_important}Salvage{/c} items to add or upgrade Aspects in your {c_important}Codex of Power{/c}.
